org.mini2Dx.core.di.annotation

Annotation Type Autowired


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Autowired
    Marks a field as injectable. By default all fields using the annotation will be required to have a value injected otherwise an exception will be thrown.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements

      boolean required
      Declares whether the annotated dependency is required.
